193
00:19:25,986 --> 00:19:31,322
Everyday, the old man
spoke of his country.

194
00:19:31,458 --> 00:19:32,891
Cric!

195
00:19:33,027 --> 00:19:34,153
Crac!

196
00:19:34,295 --> 00:19:35,353
Misticric!

197
00:19:35,496 --> 00:19:37,293
Misticrac!

198
00:19:45,139 --> 00:19:48,802
