were empty."

234
00:22:08,215 --> 00:22:10,877
"The Master had become
the Boss!"

235
00:22:11,018 --> 00:22:14,886
"So I stayed on, like all
the other blacks"

236
00:22:15,022 --> 00:22:17,513
